        "text": "With all the onstage magic happening in \"Death Becomes Her,\" it's enough to make your head spin. Adapted from The 1994 camo Classic starring MervI Streep and Goldie Hawn, the lavish new brodewav musical serves uo Wevereni with dumbfounding feats of neatrical sorcery.",
