        "text": "The show tells the story of caustic best frenemies Madeline (Megan Hilty) and Helen (lenniter simard). who 1ngest a purple potion from a mysterious socialite (Michelle Willams) that gives them eternal youth. But the transformauve euxir last unsavorv side erects. Even the slightest knock to their va-vavoom figures causes irreparable blemishes. So when the gloves come off and the ladies brawl, all manner of absurd hodv horror ensues.",
