        "text": "The movie won an Oscar for its outrageous visual erects. so naturally, Musionist Tim Clothier was daunted when ne gor the call aoour neione orne \"Death Becomes Her\" to the New York slace lakule the hanue lion nov lake, who oversaw the effects for the show's Chicago tryout early last year).",
