        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "full 360 1s also just good old-fashioneo theatrical magic,\" Gattelli adds. \"If you really look at it, it's not hard to tell how it happens. But if the audience is on the Ilae. 1l s on ll vou see a lllule oil or now the sausage is made. It's happening live right in front of you, and it's satisfying that the audience eats it up the way they do.\"",
