        "text": "From there, the musical's optical illusions only zer Whaer. Maaerne nas ner head knocked off during a shovel-wielding showdown, with the help of stunt doubles and props including an eyetricking serving cart. She also blows a hole through Helens stomach with a shotgun. Of course, unlike the movie, auolences cannor see olecur trousn Simard's torso, which instead billows smoke unroucnour ACt 4",
