        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"I was on Instagram and I saw a video of Warren literally changing his clothes while he was doing a handstand. Gattelli says. \"I was like, 'Wait a minute?' I reacneo out lo nin and was Ike. I can see a world where there's a pommel norse rouune aown a Illent or Stairs. And he was like, 'Oh, I'm all in - let's play?\"",
