        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"No one takes anything for granted,\" Gattelll says. \"It really trees everyone up, so when they do the show, they can feel confident and breathe and be funny It nelos them ler loose and sive those amazing performances - and that's always the goal.'",
