        "text": "Gattelli calls the sequence a \"true collaborative effort,\" working with lighting designer Justin 'Townsend (Moulin Rouge! The Musical\") and costume desiener raul lazewell ( Wicked to cleverly achieve the illusion that it's actually Milly ana nol lare logollie aown unio stairs. He also had to find other dancers with that particular skill set, should Yang ever need to call out of a perfor-",
