        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "The show's action centerpiece, if you will, is the Act 1 finale. In a heated conTrontauon wim Helen amnesi (Christopher Sieber), the shlubby object of both their affections. Mauernie Is Justlea down a mansion staircase, crunching her bones and mangling her limbs all the way down.",
