        "text": "\"It's an epic moment that everyone is waiting for and I was just thrilled where 1l landed. Gauell savs warren stoos the show every night with it. There are he's literally doing these handstands and cartwheels and flips. It's a total free fall and I just cannot believe he can do that.\"",
