        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "There are certainly worse TV series than \"Doc\" (Tuesdays, EST/PST, ****), which follows Dr. Amy Larsen (Molly Parker, a callous medical pro fessional who loses eight years of her memorv after a traumauc orain inturv. low characlers, vonne olots ana even offensive elements. But the sin of this particular series is one that's hard to get over: deep unpleasantness.",
