        "id": "docling_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_024_18",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"Doc\" the kids might say, cringe. It s awkward, unenjoyable and irritating. At times it's actively depressine. and not what I would classilv as",
        "bbox": [
          0.04201681163904082,
