      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_USAToday-2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_024_25",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "The concept, based on an Italian series, has potential. But \"Doc\" never does anything interesting with the plot. It's all reduced to simolistic binaries. Amnesia Amy is good, present-day Amy is ode. Huv Is a medical zenus ano ulc rest of the doctors are pale imitations. Amy loves her ex-husband, who has moved on. Amy's new fling can't tell her they were together because of office politics. It's all rather tedious",
        "bbox": [
