        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "In spite of the efforts of creator Barbie Kingman (\"Magnum, PI\"), Parker and the rest of the cast, \"Doc never coalesces into a coherent and functional TV show. It flatlines from its first few moments.",
