        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "And ultimately it's uncomfortable, ana nou in the 2o00 wav. Amv s everv 1nteraction is loaded with dramatic irony, our the audience Ish In a 2000 sool knowing that her teenage daughter actually hates her or that the new chief of internal medicine is a quack who killed a patient. We're just kind of stressed out by it.",
