        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Amy is every stereotype TV has ever developed about an unreeine doctoi Der. Her Odulens Idle Danzule out will her, but she gets results, gosh darn it. She's chief of internal medicine at a Minneapolis hospital where she annoys her ex-husband and hospital adminisTrator Michael (Omar Merwallv. stands in the way of ambitious hack Dr. Richard ler scou wol and makes ume Ioi discreet rendezvous with young hunk DI. Jake Cher Jon-Micnael Lcker)",
