        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "It's a shame, because Parker is a firstrate actress with great crealts Incluaing \"Deadwood\" and \"House of Cards.\" She is almost enough of a talent to build this creaky show around, but not quite.",
        "bbox": [
