        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "But all of that is thrown into chaos when Amy is in a car accident that leaves her with a traumatic brain injury. When she wakes up from surgery she Thinks that 1l s 201o and that she s married to Michael. She also thinks her cauculer is y ane her sou is alve. ano she is hit with major grief to learn her daughter is 17 and her son died seven",
